      <h2>Fallback to legacy (OGRS3-gen) scales for a v1 assessment</h2>
      <p>If you need either the current (OGRS4-gen) or the equivalent OGRS3 scale depending on the version of the latest assessment, use the legacyFallback option. Note that there is no fallback for Serious violent reoffending predictor, and OGP has been deprecated so should be explicitly rendered if required.</p>
      
      

  

  

  

  

