      <h2>Show legacy (OGRS3-gen) scale for a v1 assessment</h2>
      <p>Display the legacy (OGRS3-gen) scale for the latest assessment. Note that if the assessment is not legacy (v2) or there's no data for this predictor then the scales will not render. If this is not the desired behaviour you may need to add additional validation in your code.</p>

