<details class="govuk-details details--chevron-style" data-test-id="details-wrapper-combined-serious-reoffending-predictor" id="details-combined-serious-reoffending-predictor">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary" id="details-summary-combined-serious-reoffending-predictor" data-test-id="details-summary">
    <span class="details__chevron" aria-hidden="true" data-test-id="details-chevron"></span>
    <span class="details__toggle-text" data-test-id="details-toggle-text">
      <span class="details__show" data-test-id="details-show">
        Show details
        
          <span class="govuk-visually-hidden" data-test-id="details-show-hidden-text"> for the Combined serious reoffending predictor</span>
        
      </span>
      <span class="details__hide" data-test-id="details-hide">
        Hide details
        
          <span class="govuk-visually-hidden" data-test-id="details-hide-hidden-text"> for the Combined serious reoffending predictor</span>
        
      </span>
    </span>
  </summary>
  <section class="govuk-details__text"
           aria-labelledby="details-summary-combined-serious-reoffending-predictor"
           role="region"
           data-test-id="details-section">
    
          <h3>What this score predicts</h3>
          <p>
            The Combined serious reoffending predictor predicts seriously harmful offences by combining the scores from other predictors.
          </p>
          <p>
            A seriously harmful offence involves an event that is life-threatening or traumatic.
            The victim will find it difficult or impossible to recover physically or psychologically.
          </p>
          <h3>Risks combined in this score</h3>
          <p>The Combined serious reoffending predictor combines 3 different scores:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Serious violent reoffending predictor</li>
            <li>Direct contact – sexual reoffending predictor</li>
            <li>Images and indirect contact – sexual reoffending predictor</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            If a person has no history of sexual or sexually motivated offending, we base their score only on their Serious violent reoffending predictor score.
          </p>
          <p>
            Everyone gets a Serious violent reoffending predictor score, even if they have no history of violent offending.
          </p>
          <p>
            Go to the details for the Serious violent reoffending predictor and the two sexual reoffending predictors to find out:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>the offences they predict</li>
            <li>how we calculate the scores</li>
          </ul>
        
  </section>
</details>

        </div>
      
    </section>

    
