    <p>See <a href="#options-details">Nunjucks macro options</a> for more details on how to customise component.</p>
        <pre class="app-example__code"><code>{% from &quot;arns/components/predictor-timeline/macro.njk&quot; import predictorTimeline %}
    
    {{ predictorTimeline({ data: riskData }) }}</code></pre>
  
